    "Version": 14.0,
    "DisplayName": "FireEye CM",
    "Description": "FireEye Central Management (CM series) consolidates the administration, reporting and data sharing of the FireEye products in one easy-to-deploy, network-based solution. Central Management enables real-time sharing of autogenerated threat intelligence to identify and block advanced attacks targeting your organization. It also enables centralized configuration, management and reporting of FireEye solutions.",
